#: ../../source/example_gallery/complex.rst:2 c966f3cfb60043b5a50a483997b9e06a
msgid "Complex-Valued FEM — Helmholtz"
msgstr "复数值有限元方法 — Helmholtz"

#: ../../source/example_gallery/complex.rst:4 029b5250184a4cef81e4284abed3e69b
msgid ""
"A single script, ``examples/wave/helmholtz/helmholtz.py``, solves the time-"
"harmonic (frequency-domain) Helmholtz equation on the unit square with a "
"complex-valued coefficient. It is the end-to-end validation of the **complex"
" assembly path** unblocked in ROADMAP item 2: a complex element matrix now "
"flows all the way from a complex ``point_data`` coefficient, through "
"assembly and Dirichlet condensation, into a complex linear solve — and back "
"through a correct complex adjoint."
msgstr ""
"一个脚本 ``examples/wave/helmholtz/helmholtz.py`` "
"在单位正方形上求解带复数值系数的时谐(频域)Helmholtz 方程。它端到端地验证了在 ROADMAP item 2 中解锁的 "
"**复数装配路径**:复数单元矩阵现在能够从复数 ``point_data`` 系数出发,一路流经装配与狄利克雷静态凝聚,进入复数线性求解 —— "
"并通过正确的复数伴随回传。"

#: ../../source/example_gallery/complex.rst:12
#: 0bd9ef487a254aeb9e5d4743bc764dde
msgid "The strong form is the interior Helmholtz problem"
msgstr "强形式是内部 Helmholtz 问题"

#: ../../source/example_gallery/complex.rst:14
#: 0dde8ee59fa4458d8a322dd2738a92ca
#, python-brace-format
msgid ""
"-\\Delta u(x, y) \\;-\\; k^2\\, u(x, y) \\;=\\; 0\n"
"\\quad \\text{in } \\Omega = (0,1)^2,\n"
"\\qquad u = g \\text{ on } \\partial\\Omega,"
msgstr ""
"-\\Delta u(x, y) \\;-\\; k^2\\, u(x, y) \\;=\\; 0\n"
"\\quad \\text{in } \\Omega = (0,1)^2,\n"
"\\qquad u = g \\text{ on } \\partial\\Omega,"

#: ../../source/example_gallery/complex.rst:20
#: 7fbaebc38dc6472083ae2c5fc5f6165c
msgid ""
"driven entirely by the boundary data. We use the **manufactured plane-wave "
"solution**"
msgstr "完全由边界数据驱动。我们采用 **人工构造的平面波解**"

#: ../../source/example_gallery/complex.rst:23
#: fbd1f9ff970041ab9309cfd880d4e7ba
#, python-brace-format
msgid "u_\\text{exact}(x, y) \\;=\\; e^{\\,i k x},"
msgstr "u_\\text{exact}(x, y) \\;=\\; e^{\\,i k x},"

#: ../../source/example_gallery/complex.rst:27
#: d17118ab666a483f9b6466416868d634
#, python-brace-format
msgid ""
"so the Dirichlet data is :math:`g = u_\\text{exact}|_{\\partial\\Omega}`. "
"The body force is exactly zero, because :math:`-\\Delta e^{ikx} = k^2 "
"e^{ikx}` cancels the :math:`-k^2 u` mass term pointwise — which makes the "
"analytic solution available everywhere for an error check."
msgstr ""
"因此狄利克雷数据为 :math:`g = u_\\text{exact}|_{\\partial\\Omega}`\\ 。体力恰好为零,因为 "
":math:`-\\Delta e^{ikx} = k^2 e^{ikx}` 逐点抵消了 :math:`-k^2 u` 质量项 —— "
"这使得解析解在整个域上都可用于误差检验。"

#: ../../source/example_gallery/complex.rst:34
#: f0a3253f17094590991e576155c22fd8
msgid "Why a complex example matters"
msgstr "为什么复数示例很重要"

#: ../../source/example_gallery/complex.rst:36
#: 862e1e1486b047bea8aec2010a613ad7
msgid ""
"Everything in the assembly stack used to assume a real dtype. Helmholtz is "
"the smallest problem that exercises the complex path end to end:"
msgstr "装配栈过去处处假设实数 dtype。Helmholtz 是端到端演练复数路径的最小问题:"

#: ../../source/example_gallery/complex.rst:39
#: 548a8b9ccb0c4d7db5749bdc7f02ab63
msgid ""
"**Complex coefficient through** ``point_data``. The wavenumber term "
":math:`k^2` is carried as a (here constant, possibly complex) per-node field"
" and broadcast over elements and quadrature inside "
"``ElementAssembler.__call__`` — the same mechanism a PML layer will use for "
"its anisotropic, spatially-varying complex coefficients."
msgstr ""
"**复数系数经由** ``point_data``\\ 。波数项 :math:`k^2` 作为(此处为常数、可为复数的)逐节点场携带,并在 "
"``ElementAssembler.__call__`` 内部沿单元与求积广播 —— 这正是 PML "
"层用于其各向异性、随空间变化的复数系数的同一机制。"

#: ../../source/example_gallery/complex.rst:44
#: aef68c9417024ff8b540283ed7e86173
msgid ""
"**Complex Dirichlet condensation.** The boundary values :math:`g` are "
"complex, so :class:`~tensormesh.Condenser` must carry a complex inner-system"
" right-hand side."
msgstr ""
"**复数狄利克雷静态凝聚。** 边界值 :math:`g` 是复数,因此 :class:`~tensormesh.Condenser` "
"必须携带复数的内部系统右端项。"

#: ../../source/example_gallery/complex.rst:47
#: 6d6c9368fb78472c8e58282f99e32e99
#, python-brace-format
msgid ""
"**Complex linear solve.** ``SparseMatrix.solve`` delegates to ``torch-"
"sla``'s complex-symmetric :math:`LDL^\\top` / Hermitian "
":math:`LDL^\\mathsf{H}` factorisations, which also supply the matching "
"complex adjoint — essential for downstream gradient-based design."
msgstr ""
"**复数线性求解。** ``SparseMatrix.solve`` 委托给 ``torch-sla`` 的复对称 :math:`LDL^\\top` "
"/ 厄米 :math:`LDL^\\mathsf{H}` 分解,它们同时提供匹配的复数伴随 —— 这对下游基于梯度的设计至关重要。"

#: ../../source/example_gallery/complex.rst:54
#: e1fe247f659e4001888c001a73c2005b
msgid "TensorMesh setup"
msgstr "TensorMesh 设置"

#: ../../source/example_gallery/complex.rst:56
#: 734354cc68834e23aeb06497761bac1e
msgid ""
"The weak form is a single bilinear assembler; the only thing that marks it "
"as complex is the dtype cast and the complex ``k_sq`` coefficient:"
msgstr "弱形式是单个双线性装配器;唯一标记其为复数的,是 dtype 转换和复数 ``k_sq`` 系数:"

#: ../../source/example_gallery/complex.rst:59
#: 9670f6af596440629e92434c0bbbf0d2
msgid "examples/wave/helmholtz/helmholtz.py (essence)"
msgstr "examples/wave/helmholtz/helmholtz.py(精要)"

#: ../../source/example_gallery/complex.rst:85
#: 958ecb112e434d39baafbbbe20cac989
msgid "Two points worth noting:"
msgstr "两点值得注意:"

#: ../../source/example_gallery/complex.rst:87
#: ae29b5344d9f4f2f871e1c52d2e08a3c
msgid ""
"**The mesh stays real.** Geometry, shape functions, and quadrature weights "
"remain ``float64``; only the *coefficient* and the resulting system are "
"complex. ``asm.type(torch.complex128)`` promotes the assembler, and the real"
" shape-function tensors are upcast to the coefficient's complex dtype on "
"demand inside the assembly ``einsum``."
msgstr ""
"**网格保持实数。** 几何、形函数和求积权重保持 ``float64``;只有 *系数* 和由此得到的系统是复数。\\ "
"``asm.type(torch.complex128)`` 将装配器提升为复数,实数形函数张量在装配 ``einsum`` 内部按需上转换到系数的复数"
" dtype。"

#: ../../source/example_gallery/complex.rst:92
#: d455607be34d4be988ad2fa6276535fd
msgid ""
"**``complex128`` is the default.** The convergence study runs in double-"
"complex; ``--dtype complex64`` is available but, as with real FEM, double "
"precision is recommended for clean convergence rates."
msgstr ""
"**``complex128`` 是默认值。** 收敛性研究在双精度复数下运行;``--dtype complex64`` "
"可用,但与实数有限元一样,推荐使用双精度以获得干净的收敛率。"

#: ../../source/example_gallery/complex.rst:98
#: 3d1ce8782a1f4ea8bd73b608fb453eac
msgid "Convergence"
msgstr "收敛性"

#: ../../source/example_gallery/complex.rst:100
#: 1159b6e1bc1a4fc1881c4ec169c886a6
#, python-brace-format
msgid ""
"Refining the mesh drives the :math:`L^2` error against "
":math:`u_\\text{exact}` down at the expected FEM rate (modulo the usual "
"Helmholtz \"pollution\" at moderate :math:`k`). At :math:`k = 2\\pi`:"
msgstr ""
"细化网格使 :math:`L^2` 误差相对 :math:`u_\\text{exact}` 以期望的有限元速率下降(在中等 :math:`k` "
"下会有通常的 Helmholtz“污染”)。在 :math:`k = 2\\pi` 时:"

#: ../../source/example_gallery/complex.rst:115
#: 08e9512c2ef641cbbcec496072d382f4
#, python-brace-format
msgid ""
"``helmholtz.py`` output at :math:`k = 2\\pi`, :math:`h = 0.1`: the real "
"part, imaginary part, and pointwise error :math:`|u - u_\\text{exact}|` of "
"the computed field. The plane wave :math:`e^{ikx}` propagates along "
":math:`x`; the error panel stays at the discretisation floor across the "
"whole domain."
msgstr ""
"``helmholtz.py`` 在 :math:`k = 2\\pi`\\ 、\\ :math:`h = 0.1` "
"时的输出:计算所得场的实部、虚部,以及逐点误差 :math:`|u - u_\\text{exact}|`\\ 。平面波 :math:`e^{ikx}`"
" 沿 :math:`x` 传播;误差面板在整个域上保持在离散化误差下限。"

#: ../../source/example_gallery/complex.rst:123
#: e1f1f078c93243e2a64a128603273040
msgid "Cross-validation against scikit-fem"
msgstr "与 scikit-fem 的交叉验证"

#: ../../source/example_gallery/complex.rst:125
#: f444aea0507943199e83f016ff63411d
msgid ""
"The strongest correctness signal for the complex path is an independent "
"pipeline. ``tests/assemble/test_helmholtz_example.py`` hands the *same* "
"``(points, cells)`` to scikit-fem's ``MeshTri``, assembles the same form "
"with its built-in ``laplace`` / ``mass`` integrators, solves with "
"``scipy.sparse.linalg.spsolve``, and compares node by node. At :math:`h = "
"0.1`, :math:`k = 2\\pi` the two solvers agree to floating-point precision:"
msgstr ""
"复数路径最强的正确性信号是一条独立的流水线。\\ ``tests/assemble/test_helmholtz_example.py`` 把 *相同*"
" 的 ``(points, cells)`` 交给 scikit-fem 的 ``MeshTri``,用其内置的 ``laplace`` / "
"``mass`` 积分子装配同一弱形式,以 ``scipy.sparse.linalg.spsolve`` 求解,并逐节点比较。在 :math:`h ="
" 0.1`\\ 、\\ :math:`k = 2\\pi` 时,两个求解器吻合到浮点精度:"

#: ../../source/example_gallery/complex.rst:133
#: 4b2b547a3983463b9caf5a496e30489e
msgid ""
"\\frac{\\max\\,|u_\\text{tensormesh} - u_\\text{skfem}|}{\\max\\,|u|}\n"
"\\;\\approx\\; 2.3\\times10^{-15},"
msgstr ""
"\\frac{\\max\\,|u_\\text{tensormesh} - u_\\text{skfem}|}{\\max\\,|u|}\n"
"\\;\\approx\\; 2.3\\times10^{-15},"

#: ../../source/example_gallery/complex.rst:138
#: bfbeaeaa349e4d88b7d2b0de5b91cba1
#, python-brace-format
msgid ""
"i.e. machine :math:`\\varepsilon` — both pipelines inherit the *same* "
":math:`5.27\\times10^{-2}` discretisation error against the analytic plane "
"wave."
msgstr ""
"即机器 :math:`\\varepsilon` —— 两条流水线相对解析平面波继承了 *相同* 的 "
":math:`5.27\\times10^{-2}` 离散化误差。"

#: ../../source/example_gallery/complex.rst:144
#: d6a71100e24b47129d233bf145092584
msgid "Running the example"
msgstr "运行示例"

#: ../../source/example_gallery/complex.rst:155
#: e9909477a72d4fb08fc29165de2725a4
msgid "What's next"
msgstr "下一步"

#: ../../source/example_gallery/complex.rst:157
#: 9678df3db5f14e51820035ee3dbc8d00
msgid ""
"**PML scattering.** The constant scalar :math:`k^2` here is the simplest "
"complex coefficient. The same ``point_data`` channel already carries "
"anisotropic complex *tensor* coefficients, so the natural next step is a "
"perfectly-matched-layer absorbing boundary with coordinate-stretched "
":math:`A(x), c(x)` and a scattering obstacle — see ROADMAP item 2."
msgstr ""
"**PML 散射。** 此处的常标量 :math:`k^2` 是最简单的复数系数。同一 ``point_data`` 通道已经能携带各向异性的复数 "
"*张量* 系数,因此自然的下一步是带坐标拉伸 :math:`A(x), c(x)` 的完美匹配层(PML)吸收边界和一个散射障碍物 —— 见 "
"ROADMAP item 2。"

#: ../../source/example_gallery/complex.rst:163
#: c366fe1a88fb4e889d4343565543e1eb
msgid ""
"**Metamaterial topology optimization.** With the complex adjoint in place, "
"the density → SIMP → filter pipeline from :doc:`inverse_design` can be "
"driven by a wave objective (e.g. :math:`|u|^2` at a target point)."
msgstr ""
"**超材料拓扑优化。** 有了复数伴随，\\ :doc:`inverse_design` 中的密度 → SIMP → "
"滤波流水线就能由波动目标驱动(例如目标点处的 :math:`|u|^2`)。"

#: ../../source/example_gallery/complex.rst:167
#: faea314f4799498b9019812992c751ab
msgid ""
":doc:`wave` — the time-domain counterpart: the real, hyperbolic wave "
"equation with explicit central differences."
msgstr ":doc:`wave` —— 时域对应:实数、双曲的波动方程,采用显式中心差分。"
